comments: Puts her heart and soul into her work. Wholehearted. Hard worker. Caring. Beautiful soul.

I took an upper-level communications course as a non-comm major and I really enjoyed it! Some students complained about her but I didn\'t see anything wrong wit her. She cares for her students, prays with them, and expects you to learn. Her grading is a bit subjective but still a good professor.
Grades very hard but doesn\'t offer much help
Cares a lot about her students. Inspiring and knows how to motivate us. The best. Knows her stuff like nobody else.
She\'s amazing.Easy A. All her classes
